WEBVTT

00:00:00.625 --> 00:00:04.643
I am obsessed with forming
healthy communities,

00:00:04.667 --> 00:00:06.934
and that's why I started Twitch --

00:00:06.958 --> 00:00:10.393
to help people watch other people
play video games on the internet.

00:00:10.417 --> 00:00:11.726
(Laughter)

00:00:11.750 --> 00:00:13.768
Thank you for coming to my TED talk.

00:00:13.792 --> 00:00:15.351
(Laughter)

00:00:15.375 --> 00:00:17.059
So in seriousness,

00:00:17.083 --> 00:00:20.708
video games and communities
truly are quite related.

00:00:21.625 --> 00:00:24.434
From our early human history,

00:00:24.458 --> 00:00:28.018
we made our entertainment
together in small tribes.

00:00:28.042 --> 00:00:30.268
We shared stories around the campfire,